-- About the Game --
Bad Dream: Butcher is a short (10-15 minute) point&click horror game placed in a dream world. Figure your way through while trying to not lose your limbs to the Choppy-Man.

-- If you're enjoying this game, go play it for FREE! --
★Publisher: Desert Fox Software
★Play it here for free : http://gamejolt.com/games/adventure/bad-dream-butcher/20494/
